The witch can grant a creature within 30 feet a bit of good luck for 1 {g|Encyclopedia:Combat_Round}round{/g}. The target can call upon this good luck, allowing him to {g|Encyclopedia:Dice}reroll{/g}, taking the better result.
This works once per round for each of these types of checks:
- {g|Encyclopedia:Attack}attack rolls{/g}
- {g|Encyclopedia:Combat_Maneuvers}combat maneuvers{/g}
- {g|Encyclopedia:Skills}skill{/g} or {g|Encyclopedia:Ability_Scores}ability checks{/g}
- {g|Encyclopedia:Saving_Throw}saving throws{/g}
At 8th level and 16th level, the duration of this hex is extended by 1 round. Once a creature has benefited from the fortune hex, it cannot benefit from it again for 24 hours.

